  "description_text": "Nareena 5 LPM Single Flow Oxygen Concentrator\n\nNareena 5 LPM Single Flow is an Indian origin 5 LPM oxygen concentrator that supplies oxygen at the flow rate of 1-5 LPM at an oxygen purity level of 90-96% at all flow rates.\n\nWeight: Nareena 5 LPM Single Flow oxygen concentrator weighs 15 kgs.\n\nPower Consumption: This device consumes power at 550 watts \n\nSound: Nareena 5 LPM machine produces sound at 50 decibels.\n\nOxygen Purity Indicator: The machine has an inbuilt Oxygen Purity Indicator or OPI which instantly lights up in case the oxygen purity level falls below 86%.\n\nAlarms: Loss of power\n\nWarranty: The warranty period of Nareena 5 LPM Single Flow is 1year.\n\nWhat's in the Box?\n\nMachine\n\nHumidifier Bottle\n\nConnector Tube\n\nExtra Hepa & Hema Filters\n\nDust Filter\n\nExtra fuse",
